<div class="container-odd">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row text-center">
			<h1 style="font-family: 'Cookie';">Welcome to JC Auto Restoration</h1>
			<div class= "col-md-4" >
				<%= image_tag "master/parts.png", class:"icon", id:"tech1" %>
				<!--%= image_tag "master/Tech.png", onmouseover: "this.src='#{asset_path('master/Tech-hover.png')}'", onmouseout: "this.src='#{asset_path('master/Tech.png')}'", class:"icon" %-->
				<h3>Parts Retail</h3>
				<p>
					With more than 35 years in the automotive industry, JC Auto Restoration takes as much care in delivering the first-class parts you need as we do when restoring your car. Our inventory includes over 100,000 quality parts for which we have recently created an easy-to-use online store.
				</p>
				<!-- Change Tech image on hover -->
				<%= link_to "Get Parts >", "/parts", class:"button-link", onmouseover:"document.getElementById('tech1').src='#{asset_path('master/parts-hover.png')}'", onmouseout:"document.getElementById('tech1').src='#{asset_path('master/parts.png')}'" %>
				
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-4">
				<%= image_tag "master/services.png", class:"icon", id:"tech2" %>
				<h3>Restoration Services</h3>
				<p>We restore instruments, from single gauges to entire clusters, and restore unusual components of automobiles, such as the Highway Hi-Fi record players. Our experience and knowledge extends far beyond that to specialty and even exotic cars. Learn about the services we offer or inquire about your own project. (Find overview of services offered)</p>
				<!-- Change Tech image on hover -->
				<%= link_to "Get Started >", "/our-services", class:"button-link", onmouseover: "document.getElementById('tech2').src='#{asset_path('master/services-hover.png')}'", onmouseout: "document.getElementById('tech2').src='#{asset_path('master/services.png')}'" %>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-4">
				<%= image_tag "master/community.png", class:"icon", id:"tech3" %>
				<h3>MoPar Community</h3>
				<p>Aside from restoration projects we are also avid MoPar fans ourselves. We strive to be a part of the MoPar community and encourage our customers to do the same. Learn more about other MoPar fans such as yourself through our discussion boards and blogs.</p>
				<%= link_to "Get Connected >", "/community", class:"button-link", onmouseover: "document.getElementById('tech3').src='#{asset_path('master/community-hover.png')}'", onmouseout: "document.getElementById('tech3').src='#{asset_path('master/community.png')}'" %>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

